      <bioghist id="aspace_51ea04b8fe4d8a3b297b9c4b52fdf539">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>George VanTrump Burgess was born in 1903 in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. He graduated in 1925 with a degree in engineering from the Yale University Sheffield Scientific School. He died on May 3, 1979.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_6a08dcdba03f876160f093363c799809">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers consist of scrapbooks, photographs, and notebooks, documenting George VanTrump Burgess' years at Yale University and his professional career as an engineer.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
